## 📝 Mathematical Formulas Used

### Error Analysis Formulas
- **Absolute Error:** |True Value - Approximate Value|
- **Relative Error:** |True Value - Approx Value| / |True Value|
- **Percentage Error:** Relative Error × 100%
- **Round-off Error:** |Original Value - Rounded Value|
- **Error Propagation:** √(Σ(∂f/∂x_i × δx_i)²)

### Numerical Methods Formulas
- **Bisection:** c = (a + b) / 2
- **Newton-Raphson:** x_{n+1} = x_n - f(x_n)/f'(x_n)
- **False Position:** c = (a×f(b) - b×f(a)) / (f(b) - f(a))

